    <h1>Chinese Remainder Theorem</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Jim Hefferon &middot; Elementary Number Theory &middot; <a href="https://jheffero.w3.uvm.edu/numbertheory/">Ch. 5</a></p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">If moduli are pairwise coprime, a system of congruences has a unique solution mod their product. The <strong>Chinese Remainder Theorem</strong> gives a constructive algorithm to find it.</p>
    </div>

